{"tid":1263480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］城規會無視兩萬份意見 通過中環海濱改軍用碼頭","createTime":"2019-06-28T07:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T15:06:31.000Z","uid":10540,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"28d8bba504c59a1a4390936e0da6ed0da9c58f63","tid":1263480,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"2014年2月14日，城規會通過中環海濱改劃作軍用碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n政府建議，將添馬艦解放軍營對開的0.3公頃海濱用地劃為軍事用途。城規會早前收到近兩萬份意見，大部分都反對，城規會召開了歷來最大規模的16場申述會，讓有關人士陳述立場。<br />\n<br />\n政府說，過去多份公眾文件都提到會將海濱用地劃作軍用碼頭，但關注團體一直質疑規劃署誤導公眾，城規會副主席黃遠輝曾經批評政府諮詢不足。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=93071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D93071&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=0912aaf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D93071&h=28ed7581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=93071</a>"},{"pid":"3fae6bdab835e9edb6ff313b67010499c3bf52c4","tid":1263480,"uid":447,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T08:13:56.000Z","msg":"香港人 我地而家基本訴求一個都達唔到<br />\n冇撤回<br />\n冇成立黑警調查組<br />\n冇還到義士清白<br />\n冇撤銷暴動<br />\n<br />\n有人擋喺你前面捱打同死諫<br />\n有人坐完政治監出返嚟都要再努力<br />\n有人喺獄中幾希望可以真正地參與其中<br />\n<br />\n你有咩原因唔出嚟！<br />\n你有咩原因鬆懈！<br />\n你有咩原因唔為自己好好真正地爭取！<br />\n<br />\n時代革命，光復香港！<br />\n<br />\n大家記得今晚帶餐具去野餐！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7f87a2f71e958cd7a1e31e265f2e22ddfbe0bec6","tid":1263480,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd247ef2713935d8a74e54814ea6bd4a72981600","tid":1263480,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:25:09.0